            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the butternut squash is tender, remove the tray[s] from the oven and transfer the <strong>cooked squash</strong> to the risotto and stir it all together</p><p>Transfer the <strong>crispy bacon</strong> to a clean chopping board and chop roughly – these are your <strong>crispy bacon bits</strong></p>",
